def description_analysis2(variable,data):
    
    Nbr = data['nbrtotc'].groupby([data[variable]]).sum().reset_index()
    exp = data[['duree']].groupby([data[variable]]).sum().reset_index()
    charge = data[['chargtot']].groupby([data[variable]]).sum().reset_index()
    obs = pd.merge(Nbr,exp)
    obs = pd.merge(obs,charge)
    obs['Freq']=obs['nbrtotc']/obs['duree']
    obs['AVG']=obs['chargtot']/obs['nbrtotc']
    
    table=obs
    
    #frequency plot
    plt.rcParams['figure.figsize'] = [20, 6]
    table_to_plot=table.loc[:,[variable,'duree','Freq']]
    table_to_plot[variable]=table_to_plot[variable].astype("category")
    table_to_plot.plot(kind='bar', secondary_y='duree', rot=30)
    plt.xticks(range(table_to_plot.shape[0]),list(table_to_plot.iloc[:,0]), rotation=30)
    plt.title('Frequency')
    plot=plt.show()
    
    #severity plot
    plt.rcParams['figure.figsize'] = [20, 6]
    table_to_plot=table.loc[:,[variable,'duree','AVG']]
    table_to_plot[variable]=table_to_plot[variable].astype("category")
    table_to_plot.plot(kind='bar', secondary_y='duree', rot=30)
    plt.xticks(range(table_to_plot.shape[0]),list(table_to_plot.iloc[:,0]), rotation=30)
    plt.title('Severity')
    plot=plt.show()
    
    return(obs)
